# Mental Health Detection & Support System

AI-powered emotion recognition system using deep learning to detect emotions from facial expressions.

## Features
- Real-time emotion detection from images
- 7 emotion classes (happy, sad, angry, fear, surprise, disgust, neutral)
- AI chatbot for mental health support
- Analytics and insights

## Usage
1. Upload an image
2. Click "Analyze" to detect emotions
3. Chat with the AI assistant for support
4. View analytics on your emotional patterns
